    <item>
      <title>欧洲股票随着特朗普的关税打击饮料公司而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/european-stocks-drop-as-trade-tensions-weigh-ahead-of-us-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）威胁要对欧盟的酒精饮料征收200％关税之后，欧洲股票倾斜的贸易倾斜，饮料制造商滑行，这表明跨大西洋贸易战正在升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/european-stocks-drop-as-trade-tensions-weigh-ahead-of-us-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 08:18:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票昏昏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票的三周逐渐减少了，再次将S＆amp; p 500发送到10％校正的悬崖上。另一份良性通货膨胀报告激发了唐纳德·特朗普总统贸易战的新鲜萨尔沃，这激发了乐观，并激发了国库中对避风港的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 22:32:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
